      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOOSEBUMPS RICO (4) was quickly out of the boxes with a slick early sectional clocking 24.18 with a head win at this track over 425m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Great chance again. MOTIVATE (2) was a big winner in quick time then came home hard into third and beaten 6 lengths at this track (24.70) last time. Hard to beat again. MIA BLONDE (6) finds it hard to break through. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when third (24.42) at this track. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. SMILING BEE (1) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
